    comp_list

    comp_list.Rmd


    library(saferTool)


    Datasets 

    list1 <- list(a = 1:5, b = LETTERS[1:2], d = matrix(1:6)) # list
list2 <- list(1:5, LETTERS[1:2]) # list
list3 <- list(a = 1:5, b = LETTERS[1:2]) # list
list4 <- list(LETTERS[5:9], matrix(1:6), 1:5) # list
